   example entry for analog device
   ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

added by Your Name <your@email>

Action            | Event            | Values ([a]nalog / [d]igital)
------------------+------------------+---------------------------------------
Left                Axis 1 low         [a] 0 to -32767

