#############################################################################


   Super Nintendo Joypad
   ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

added by Christian Garbs <mitch@uni.de>

(on parallel port, see /usr/src/linux/Documentation/joystick-parport.txt)

Action            | Event            | Values ([a]nalog / [d]igital)
------------------+------------------+----------------------------------------
Left                Axis 1 low         [d] -32767
Right               Axis 1 high        [d]  32767
Up                  Axis 2 low         [d] -32767
Down                Axis 2 high        [d]  32767
Button "A"          Button 1
Button "B"          Button 2
Button "X"          Button 3
Button "Y"          Button 4
Button "L"          Button 5
Button "R"          Button 6
Button "Select"     Button 7
Button "Start"      Button 8


